{
  "stem": "964.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that time, our clothes from [NON-ENGLISH] came in from-- civilian clothes was all fallen apart, so the Germans give us their working clothes, their [NON-ENGLISH], the one piece, you know?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like an overall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Overalls.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had some hats from Germans, but not the insignias, or this kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we spoke good German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we paraded as Germans almost.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, we came out on the highway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We spoke good German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That Jakob [NON-ENGLISH] picked up his finger and stop the trucks which was coming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They picked up soldiers, you know, hitchhiking on the way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he stopped the truck and we asked the guy, where are you going?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, I'm going to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was about 40 kilometers before Dneprodzerzhinsk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is the huge [NON-ENGLISH] that the communists build it in 1935, I think it was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a huge piece of propaganda that the [NON-ENGLISH] was building that [NON-ENGLISH], like the hydroelectric station.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and on the way, the MP, so to speak, in English way, was stopping the trucks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they didn't stop the truck to-- to-- to check what they're carrying.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they stopped if the driver had a license to go from here to there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything had to be documented.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they checked just the driver, and they didn't look in the back, and we went.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So very often, they stopped the trucks on the way and we passed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We came into [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The guy said, that's it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You have to get off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We got off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He said, you look over there and maybe you get a truck to Dneprodzerzhinsk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we're looking around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We found the truck to Dneprodzerzhinsk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Also, everything in German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We spoke in German and everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
